---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 106
  - Title: Christ in Islâm
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Phantom Flux of Life
---
Jesus, son of Mary (Peace be upon him!), said, ‘By God, the world has not
settled in the heart of a worshipper without three of its things sticking to
it： labour whose distress does not cease, poverty which does not catch up on
its wealth, and hope which does not attain its goal.'
